    "body": "## Steps to reproduce\r\n1. Open a few websites and disable ETP in order to add them to the exceptions list;\r\n2. Got to Settings -> Privacy & Security -> Exceptions;\r\n3. Tap the Remove all websites button.\r\n\r\n### Expected behavior\r\nAfter removing all websites from the exceptions list the Exceptions button should become grey.\r\n### Actual behavior\r\nAfter removing all websites from the exceptions list the Exceptions button can be tapped once more resulting in a flicker before becoming grey.\r\n### Device information\r\n\r\n* Android devices: Oppo Find X3 (Android 11), OnePlus 6T (Android 9), Huawei P9 Lite (Android 8)\r\n* Focus version: RC 94.1.1\r\n\r\nhttps://user-images.githubusercontent.com/50983519/139405890-ca9eeb5e-3280-45cf-a930-d601b5a7e5a7.mp4\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n",
